16:38.031 --> 16:40.698
♪ Treat me fine,
walk the chalk line ♪

16:40.782 --> 16:42.573
♪ And stay on my mind ♪

16:42.657 --> 16:44.989
♪ He's got to be all right ♪

16:45.073 --> 16:46.198
♪ Fight all night ♪

16:46.281 --> 16:47.782
♪ Mama will do the rest ♪

16:47.865 --> 16:49.531
♪ Now how 'bout that, Miss? ♪

16:49.615 --> 16:51.323
♪ He's got to do
what he's told ♪

16:51.406 --> 16:53.323
♪ And bring sweet mama
that gold ♪

16:53.406 --> 16:56.490
♪ To satisfy my soul ♪

16:56.573 --> 16:59.782
♪ ♪

16:59.865 --> 17:02.490
Oh, yeah!

17:02.573 --> 17:04.989
Yes!

17:05.073 --> 17:07.281
There you go!

