1:08:03.323 --> 1:08:05.281
children: Bad Robot.

1:08:08.823 --> 1:08:10.323
[bright tone]

1:08:13.907 --> 1:08:16.198
Dinner will be served
in 15 minutes.

1:08:16.948 --> 1:08:18.073
Don't mind the others.

1:08:18.156 --> 1:08:19.823
Just because they don't want
you here,

1:08:20.948 --> 1:08:22.698
doesn't mean
you're not supposed to be.

1:08:24.156 --> 1:08:25.698
♪ (INTENSE MUSIC PLAYS) ♪

1:08:26.073 --> 1:08:30.323
The secret birthright
Pop wrote about is real.

1:08:32.239 --> 1:08:34.989
CHRISTINA BRAITHWHITE:
Our destiny's not decided by
our families.

1:08:36.823 --> 1:08:38.156
You just have to seize it.

1:08:39.698 --> 1:08:42.531
I thought the world was one way
and I found out it isn't...

1:08:44.448 --> 1:08:45.989
and it terrifies me.

1:08:47.573 --> 1:08:48.657
(SCREAMS)

1:08:52.823 --> 1:08:54.740
I thought I had everything
I wanted...

1:08:56.740 --> 1:09:01.573
only to discover power
like I've never known before.

1:09:01.657 --> 1:09:03.531
♪ You cannot escape it ♪

1:09:05.365 --> 1:09:07.323
WOMAN: It's a rat race
to the finish

1:09:08.198 --> 1:09:09.573
and it's winner takes all.

1:09:10.782 --> 1:09:13.323
LETITIA LEWIS: We gotta face
this new world head on

1:09:14.782 --> 1:09:16.531
and stake our claim in it.

1:09:18.907 --> 1:09:20.031
It's our story.

1:09:21.531 --> 1:09:24.073
This birthright belongs to
our family.

1:09:24.698 --> 1:09:26.406
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪
